{"id": 3113, "genre": 1001, "title": "社交网络都给你带来了哪些额外的“社会性死亡”体验？", "description": "那些尴尬到无以复加的线上“被公开”场景。（题图来自：iStock ©️ greyj ）", "record_count": 1181, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200104213640NuspCAWnm8lPayko.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-04T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351488, "content": "小号被朋友看到，写满阴暗话语爆裂情绪的小号，所有被偷窥的恐惧统统爆发", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474072}, {"id": 351489, "content": "已读不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544695}, {"id": 351491, "content": "只会哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114039}, {"id": 351493, "content": "可以可以\r\n666", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650619}, {"id": 351494, "content": "群里说完话就冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 184, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318584}, {"id": 351495, "content": "留下了浏览记录却没有点赞或评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 883151}, {"id": 351498, "content": "饿了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676451}, {"id": 351756, "content": "朋友们出去聚会发朋友圈，却没有喊我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511406}, {"id": 351516, "content": "匿名人设的微博小号被母上摸到并关注", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676469}, {"id": 351518, "content": "想改自己在群里的名称结果把群名称改成了自己的名字", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758606}, {"id": 351521, "content": "朋友翻出了以前学生时代qq空间的状态截图发到小群里，啊，当代凌迟之刑", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676495}, {"id": 351522, "content": "已读不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676249}, {"id": 351523, "content": "在工作群里表白（实际发错了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5109}, {"id": 351525, "content": "工作聚餐，甲方领导说 唉你来点餐吧看你大众点评经常发东西呢！（万恶的自动读取通讯录加好友）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676515}, {"id": 351528, "content": "好友列表全部是躺尸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427752}, {"id": 351531, "content": "想撤回却点到删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676538}, {"id": 351549, "content": "追星微博号被熟人发现", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103270}, {"id": 351550, "content": "这条评论没人点赞 于是自己手动给了自己一个赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103270}, {"id": 351551, "content": "很久以前的聊天记录被翻出，一脸惊讶的我不禁感叹，真是我说的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852421}, {"id": 352321, "content": "我本很活跃，但长时间没有收到回复的消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351593, "content": "发色色图片发错群啊哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 351599, "content": "当然是只有找我借钱的时候好友列表理人才会活过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332426}, {"id": 351616, "content": "只看不评论\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676133}, {"id": 352385, "content": "群聊里最后一个发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1682501}, {"id": 352229, "content": "朋友圈被评论时如何回复......", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1678960}, {"id": 351721, "content": "收到不想回的消息，疯狂吐槽，对面：对方正在输入……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676993}, {"id": 351468, "content": "被认识但不熟的人找到了自己的小号", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351469, "content": "想要群发结果把一堆人拉了个群", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351470, "content": "手误戳错表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351471, "content": "偷看自己暗恋的人留下了访问记录无法删除", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351475, "content": "“对不起，刚才号被盗了……”", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655378}, {"id": 351477, "content": "已读不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 285, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544180}, {"id": 351479, "content": "发圈后一小时仍无任何人评论或点赞，慌张检查，发现分组选错...", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454108}, {"id": 351482, "content": "朋友圈屏蔽了家人没有屏蔽陌生人，被没加好友的亲戚发现了谈恋爱的证据", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212252}, {"id": 351483, "content": "装熟人骗我钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676375}, {"id": 351484, "content": "私信内容手快发到工作群。", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368553}]}